  <entry>
    <title>最大子段和问题</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%90%E6%AE%B5%E5%92%8C%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>常规思想就是两重或者三重循环。但显然可以更简单一点：</p>
<h3 id="分治法"><a href="#分治法" class="headerlink" title="分治法"></a>分治法</h3><p>将最大子段a[1:n]分为a[1:n/2]和a[n/2+1:n]两段，那么就有三种情况：  </p>
<ol>
<li>最大子段和在a[1:n]上，设其为s1</li>
<li>最大子段和在a[n/2+1:n]上，设其为s2</li>
<li>最大子段和就是a[n]的最大子段和，即s1+s2<br>此时时间复杂度为O(nlogn)<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">MaxSubSum</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> left, <span class="keyword">int</span> right)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> sum = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (left==right) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sum = a[left]&gt;<span class="number">0</span> ? a[left] : <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> center = (left + right) / <span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">// 划分</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> leftsum = MaxSubSum(a, left, center); <span class="comment">// 子情况1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> rightsum = MaxSubSum(a, center + <span class="number">1</span>, right); <span class="comment">// 子情况2</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> s1 = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> lefts = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = center; i &gt;= left; i--) &#123; <span class="comment">// 子情况3</span></span><br><span class="line">            lefts += a[i];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (lefts &gt; s1) s1 = lefts;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> s2 = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> right = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = center+<span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= right; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            rights += a[i];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (rights &gt; s2) s2 = rights;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        sum = s1 + s2;</span><br><span class="line">        sum = <span class="built_in">max</span>(leftsum, rightsum, sum);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> sum;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>大整数乘法</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%E4%B9%98%E6%B3%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>大整数乘法(n位2进制)X*Y可以采用归并的思想解决。<br>将X按位数划分成两半，高位为a，低位为b：<br>$$ X = a * 2^(n/2) + b $$<br>同样的，将Y按位数分成两半，高位为c，低位为d：<br>$$ Y = c * 2^(n/2) + d $$<br>这样$ XY = ac * 2^(n) + (ad + bc) * 2(n/2) + bd $，然而很容易发现，$ T(n) = 4T(n-1) + O(n) $ （这里的4为ac,ad,bc,bd四次T(n-1)的乘法）<strong>时间复杂度没有改进！</strong><br>那么优化一下：$ XY = ac * 2^(n) + ((a-b)(d-c) + ac + bd) * 2(n/2) + bd $，这样一来，表面上看起来更烦了，但相比起上面，这个式子只要计算(a-b)(d-c),ac,bd 三次T(n-1)的乘法，比上面的式子花的时间更少了，为啥用(a-b)(d-c)不用(a+b)(d+c)呢？显然减比加的位数要少。</p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>残缺棋盘问题</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/%E6%AE%8B%E7%BC%BA%E6%A3%8B%E7%9B%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>残缺棋盘是一个有2k*2k(k≥1)个方格的棋盘，其中恰有一个方格残缺。要对其用四种三格板（L形骨牌）进行覆盖。  </p>
</blockquote>
<p>用分治法解决挺容易的。显然每块大棋盘都可以划分成4块k*k个方块的小棋盘，8块(k/2)*(k/2)个方块的更小棋盘，以此类推……<br>但问题是，每次分治划分出来的棋盘只有一块是残缺的，另外三块并不是。那么就要给另外三块制造一些残缺性。<br>最简单的是：<strong>在非残缺棋盘的相邻拐角处放置一块三格版</strong>，这样每块小棋盘都拥有残缺性啦！<br>这样就满足分治法的要求了，大问题能分成一样的小问题，小问题的解也能拼凑成大问题的解。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">chessBoard</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> tr, <span class="keyword">int</span> tc, <span class="keyword">int</span> dr, <span class="keyword">int</span> dc, <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="built_in">size</span>)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="comment">// tr,tc为棋盘边界，dr,dc为残缺块位置 </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">size</span>==<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span>; <span class="comment">// 递归出口，1*1的就免了</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> t = tile++; <span class="comment">// L型骨牌号</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> s = <span class="built_in">size</span> / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 左上角棋盘子问题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (dr&lt;tr+s &amp;&amp; dc&lt;tc+s) &#123; <span class="comment">// 残缺方格在此棋盘中</span></span><br><span class="line">        chessBoard(tr, tc, dr, dc, s);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123; <span class="comment">// 残缺方格不在此棋盘中</span></span><br><span class="line">        board[tr+s<span class="number">-1</span>][tc+s<span class="number">-1</span>] = t; <span class="comment">// 用t号L型骨牌覆盖右下角</span></span><br><span class="line">        chessBoard(tr, tc, tr+s<span class="number">-1</span>, tc+s<span class="number">-1</span>, s); <span class="comment">// 子问题求解</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 左下角棋盘子问题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 右上角棋盘子问题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 右下角棋盘子问题</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>归并排序</title>
    <url>/2020/03/30/%E5%BD%92%E5%B9%B6%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>归并排序本质上是一次自顶向下的二分分割，分割后的n个单元素子问题的两两合并的过程<br>类比同样是树形结构的二分查找的时间复杂度是O(logn)，加上一个合并的过程就成为了归并排序，其复杂度就应该是O(nlogn)<br>但是本质上划分并没有意义，因为可以将原来的数组就看成一个已经划分成单元素子问题的集合，所以简而言之：<strong>并不需要递归过程，直接可以从树的底部开始向上合并</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Merge</span><span class="params">(Type a[], Type b[], <span class="keyword">int</span> left, <span class="keyword">int</span> mid, <span class="keyword">int</span> right)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = left; <span class="comment">// 左数组待比较游标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> j = mid + <span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">// 右数组待比较游标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> k = left; <span class="comment">// 合并数组的游标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (i&lt;=mid &amp;&amp; j&lt;=right) &#123; <span class="comment">// 在i,j有一个越界以后，循环即终止</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (a[i] &lt; a[j]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>快速排序</title>
    <url>/2020/03/26/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>快速排序<strong>仍然采用了分治法的思想</strong>，只是在其基础上引入了哨兵，实现了<strong>跨度更大</strong>的交换。因此，主程序实现用递归显得更加简单和清晰。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">QuickSort</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (q &lt; r) &#123; <span class="comment">// 仅仅确保它是个合法数组</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> q = Partition(a, p, r); <span class="comment">// 表面切分数组，获得哨兵q的位置与一个全部比q小的数组切分，一个全部比q大的数组切分</span></span><br><span class="line">        QuickSort(a, p, q<span class="number">-1</span>); <span class="comment">// 子问题求解</span></span><br><span class="line">        QuickSort(a, q+<span class="number">1</span>, r);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>很显然Partition是这个算法的精髓。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Partition</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = p;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> j = r + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x = a[p];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(True) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (a[++i] &lt; x); <span class="comment">// 找到比x大或等于x的左边区元素下标，准备换到右边</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (a[--j] &gt; x); <span class="comment">// 找到比x小或等于x的右边区元素下标，准备换到左边</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 上面造成的结果就是标兵与比其大/小元素反复左右大跨度交换，i和j下标对应的元素交替为标兵</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (i &gt;= j) <span class="keyword">break</span>; <span class="comment">// 这一句放在实际交换之前，i = j时将陷入死循环，i,j都为标兵的最终位置，必须退出</span></span><br><span class="line">        swap(a[i], a[j]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> j; <span class="comment">// 也可以return i</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>不过想一想，每次都初始化同一个哨兵位置是最合理的吗？显然不是，当分治时一边为0个元素，中间为哨兵，另一边为n-1个元素时，陷入了最坏的情况，与插入排序差不多慢，算法导论上有详细的说明。<strong>所以可以增加一点随机性去规避极端性</strong>：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">RandomizedPartition</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = Random(p, r);</span><br><span class="line">    Swap(a[i], a[p]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Partition(a, p, r)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>快速排序在常数倍分割时时间复杂度为O(nlogn)，在最坏条件下（一边为0个元素，中间为哨兵，另一边为n-1个元素）时，时间复杂度为O(n^2)</p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>操作系统实验 - lab0</title>
    <url>/2020/03/08/%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%20-%20lab0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<h3 id="Exercise-1-在fibo-c中使用c语言实现输出斐波那契数列前n位的程序（n为评测时的输入数据，输出用空格分隔，例如1-1-2-3-5）"><a href="#Exercise-1-在fibo-c中使用c语言实现输出斐波那契数列前n位的程序（n为评测时的输入数据，输出用空格分隔，例如1-1-2-3-5）" class="headerlink" title="Exercise 1 在fibo.c中使用c语言实现输出斐波那契数列前n位的程序（n为评测时的输入数据，输出用空格分隔，例如1 1 2 3 5）"></a>Exercise 1 在fibo.c中使用c语言实现输出斐波那契数列前n位的程序（n为评测时的输入数据，输出用空格分隔，例如1 1 2 3 5）</h3></blockquote>
<h3 id="源程序"><a href="#源程序" class="headerlink" title="源程序"></a><strong>源程序</strong></h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Fabonacci</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (n == <span class="number">1</span> || n == <span class="number">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> Fabonacci(n<span class="number">-1</span>) + Fabonacci(n<span class="number">-2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i,n;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>,&amp;n);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(i = <span class="number">1</span>;i &lt;= n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d "</span>,Fabonacci(i));</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a><strong>思路</strong></h3><p>使用递归生成Fabonacci数列后输出</p>
<blockquote>
<h3 id="Exercise-2-完善Makefile，要求用make指令可实现fibo-c的编译链接，可执行文件名为fibo"><a href="#Exercise-2-完善Makefile，要求用make指令可实现fibo-c的编译链接，可执行文件名为fibo" class="headerlink" title="Exercise 2 完善Makefile，要求用make指令可实现fibo.c的编译链接，可执行文件名为fibo"></a>Exercise 2 完善Makefile，要求用make指令可实现fibo.c的编译链接，可执行文件名为fibo</h3></blockquote>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a><strong>代码</strong></h3><figure class="highlight mk"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">all: fibo.c</span></span><br><span class="line">	gcc -o fibo fibo.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="注意点"><a href="#注意点" class="headerlink" title="注意点"></a><strong>注意点</strong></h3><p>每一个指令前必须有一个TAB，而非4个或两个空格</p>
<blockquote>
<h3 id="Exercise-3-在文件夹sh-test中新建文件hello-os-sh，要求通过指令bash-hello-os-sh-file-hello-os-c-可以在当前为文件夹下生成hello-os-c，其内容为file的第8、32、128、512、1024-行的内容提取。"><a href="#Exercise-3-在文件夹sh-test中新建文件hello-os-sh，要求通过指令bash-hello-os-sh-file-hello-os-c-可以在当前为文件夹下生成hello-os-c，其内容为file的第8、32、128、512、1024-行的内容提取。" class="headerlink" title="Exercise 3 在文件夹sh_test中新建文件hello_os.sh，要求通过指令bash hello_os.sh file hello_os.c 可以在当前为文件夹下生成hello_os.c，其内容为file的第8、32、128、512、1024 行的内容提取。"></a>Exercise 3 在文件夹sh_test中新建文件hello_os.sh，要求通过指令bash hello_os.sh file hello_os.c 可以在当前为文件夹下生成hello_os.c，其内容为file的第8、32、128、512、1024 行的内容提取。</h3></blockquote>
<h3 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a><strong>代码</strong></h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line">sed -e 8w<span class="variable">$2</span> -e 32w<span class="variable">$2</span> -e 128w<span class="variable">$2</span> -e 512w<span class="variable">$2</span> -e 1024w<span class="variable">$2</span> <span class="variable">$1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="思路-1"><a href="#思路-1" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a><strong>思路</strong></h3><p>连续使用<code>sed -e [行号]w[目标文件名] [源文件名]</code>指令复制生成</p>
<h3 id="nbsp"><a href="#nbsp" class="headerlink" title="&nbsp;"></a>&nbsp;</h3><blockquote>
<h3 id="Exercise-4-拷贝文件"><a href="#Exercise-4-拷贝文件" class="headerlink" title="Exercise 4 拷贝文件"></a>Exercise 4 拷贝文件</h3></blockquote>
<h3 id="指令"><a href="#指令" class="headerlink" title="指令"></a><strong>指令</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp [选项] 源文件 目标文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<h3 id="实验环境下Git的使用"><a href="#实验环境下Git的使用" class="headerlink" title="实验环境下Git的使用"></a>实验环境下Git的使用</h3></blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">获取Git服务器IP: cat .cgconfig</span><br><span class="line">克隆远程仓库: git clone git@IP:$CGUSERID-lab</span><br><span class="line">打开仓库: cd 181303216-lab</span><br><span class="line">查看分支: git branch -a</span><br><span class="line">检出分支: git checkout ...</span><br><span class="line">添加文件至暂存区: git add ...</span><br><span class="line">提交所有更改: git commit -all</span><br><span class="line">提交: git push</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
